d=E2=80=99s compensation until the full amount was repaid.=E2=80=9D Honestl=
y that is not how prop trading is supposed to work! If you=E2=80=99re tradi=
ng with your employer=E2=80=99s money, and you lose it, and they take it ou=
t of your paycheck, in what sense were you ever really trading with your em=
ployer=E2=80=99s money?=C2=A0
