ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
 think a lot</a> about questions of <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/25241118.274768/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlua=
