who commissioned the law firm are no longer with the company.</p></blockquo=
te><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In general if you are the CEO of a company =
it is bad when the board is unhappy enough to commission a fancy law firm t=
o =E2=80=9Cconduct a review of the company=E2=80=99s business activities.=
=E2=80=9D One approach might be to try to make the board happier. But possi=
bly the better approach is to make the board=C2=A0<em>unhappier</em>, so th=
ey say =E2=80=9Cnever mind, I=E2=80=99ve seen enough=E2=80=9D and you don=
=E2=80=99t have to do the review? We are talking about making the best of a=
 bad situation here and this is definitely a creative solution.</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
