r: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">here=E2=80=
=99s a wild anecdote</a> about Watson allegedly throwing a book at an emplo=
yee:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One anonymous staffer told=
 me Watson literally threw a book across the room at her. The book was <em>=
The Hard Thing About Hard Things: Building a Business When There Are No Eas=
