umber generator, it will go down a lot, you will have a big tax loss, and t=
hen it will go up a lot again the next day and you won=E2=80=99t have a=C2=
=A0<em>real=C2=A0</em>loss.=E2=80=9D That=E2=80=99s a good product!=C2=A0</=
p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Obviously my product is better =E2=80=94=C2=
