e=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration:=
 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> reading</a> of Gensler=
=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/2524111=
8.274768/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9zZWNzLWdlbnNsZXItYWltcy10by=
