 the above=E2=80=9D and that if he could wave a magic wand he=E2=80=99d pro=
bably want to ban retail internalization, dark pools, everything. But that =
seems like a pretty hard thing to do and my guess is that=C2=A0if the SEC e=
ver actually does anything here =E2=80=94=C2=A0not all=C2=A0<em>that=C2=A0<=
/em>likely? =E2=80=94=C2=A0it will be more like banning payment for order f=
