 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">that would be fine for =
Robinhood</a>.) But I don=E2=80=99t know and I suspect nobody else does eit=
her.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Citadel Securities has a large busines=
s of market-making for retail orders, and that business appears to be good =
and lucrative, and I guess if the SEC banned it that would be bad for Citad=
el Securities? (I mean, it=E2=80=99d be fine, the retail orders would go to=
 the lit exchanges, and Citadel Securities would compete to fill them, and =
