but there's a reason Citadel Securities wants to get those retail orders se=
parately.) But if the SEC forbade Citadel Securities from=C2=A0<em>paying=
=C2=A0</em>for those orders, that would obviously be good for Citadel Secur=
ities? Because getting things free is better than paying for them? <a href=
