m securities regulators.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CPayment f=
or order flow is a cost to me,=E2=80=9D Griffin said, addressing The Econom=
ic Club of Chicago on Monday. =E2=80=9CSo if you=E2=80=99re going to tell m=
e that by regulatory fiat one of my major items of expense disappears, I=E2=
=80=99m OK with that.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"=
>Yeah seems right. But Bloomberg News <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomber=
gbusiness.com/click/25241118.274768/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXd=
